{"tid":441404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下自己中小學遇過嘅教畜仆街史","createTime":"2017-10-19T15:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T16:35:34.000Z","uid":153933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0823847e78774ad59dd77fe38cc4dabcd34e28","tid":441404,"uid":153933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣好興傳紙仔傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一日上堂 同坐後邊嘅女同學傳紙仔<br />\n好小學雞咁傾下人地壞話是非嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後比個教畜發現左<br />\n佢就搶左張紙仔係到睇<br />\n冷笑左一下<br />\n然後...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢用投影機投射出黎比哂全班睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明傳紙仔係充滿童真嘅野<br />\n點解要玩鳩啲學生<br />\n搞到我比人杯葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全係童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死教畜 傳紙仔關你撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04a0dbb1410a209df72ed404dbeed5a95aa145b","tid":441404,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"捉鳩我抄人功課 食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eace0b7d441aac70baa626e42a05796d51420f6c","tid":441404,"uid":153933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉鳩我抄人功課 食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我比人抄功課 然後話我抄人功課<br />\n比條仆街罰抄<br />\n諗起都嬲嬲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dcc4bc482bd744d536a9f52eef10abdeb8af69","tid":441404,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci